CustomField.description: Sets the maximum number of Assignment ids allowed to be passed in via the global invocable class Invoke_RateCalcCreation so as to control the apex batch size for creation of employee specific rate calculators. If left blank a default batch size of 5 will be applied.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Sets the maximum number of Assignment ids allowed to be passed in via the global invocable class Invoke_RateCalcCreation so as to control the apex batch size for creation of employee specific rate calculators. If left blank a default batch size of 5 will be applied.
CustomField.label: Invoke Rate Calc Creation Batch Size
